OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,6,FCloudy on Thursday with rain in the
OL,7,Fmorning, and again later in the day.
OL,8,FDry with sunny spells on Friday.
OL,9,FMainly dry on Saturday. Warm.
